title: [UCC] San Fransisco Comics 1-7, 1970-1981
description:
[UCC] San Fransisco Comics 1-7, 1970-1981 

Another classic Underground Comic Serie featuring contributions by masters of the art such as Crumb, Shelton and Griffith, among many others. 

For a short briefing on Underground Comics go here: <a href="
http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Underground_comics" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">
http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Underground_comics</a>

For a detailed history of the underground comics revolution read this book: <a href="
http://books.google.com/books?id=hQb_q6DWle4C&printsec=frontcover&hl=da&source=gbs_v2_summary_r&cad=0" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">
http://books.google.com/books?id=hQb_q6DWle4C&printsec=frontcover&hl=da&source=gbs_v2_summary_r&cad=0</a>

This Torrent includes:

San Fransisco Comics Vol 1 No. 1 - Jan-Feb 1970
Rory Hayes, Ric Sloane, Willy Murphy, Larry Welz, S. Clay Wilson, Dan O'Neill, Rifas, Jim Osborne, Spain, Mervinius, R. Crumb, Rick Griffin, Jaxon, Robert Dougherty, Dave Sheridan.

San Fransisco Comics Vol 1 No. 2 - March-April
Rick Griffin, Willy Murphy, Greg Irons, Robert Williams, Kim Dietch, Jim Osborne, Spain Rodriguez, Trina, Robert Williams, Robert Crumb, Dan O'Neill, Larry Welz, Mervinius, S. Clay Wilson, Ph.D. & William Gaines, Al Feldstein, Johnny Craig, Jack Davis, Reed Crandall, Bill Elder, George Evans, Frank Frazetta, Graham Ingels, Jack Kamen, Roy Krenkel, Bernie Krigstein, Harvey Kurtzman, Joe Orlando, John Severin, Al Williamson, Wally Wood and Basil Wolverton.

K. Dietch, Irons, Spain, Wilson, W. Murphy, Trina, W. Mendes, Osborne, R. Crumb, J. Green, Geo Metzger, Mervinius, Robt. Williams, R. Hayes, J. Hayes, G. Shelton, S. Diettch, J. Beck, J. Lynch, G. Arlington

San Fransisco Comics Vol 1 No. 4 - 1973
Roger Brand, Landon Chesney, R. Crumb, Kim Deitch, Justin Green, Bill Griffith, Larry Hallgren, Jeffrey Hayes, R. Hint, R. Hinge, R. Hayes, Gary King, Jay Kinney, Leslie, Bobby London, Jay Lynch, McMillan, Willy Murphy, Jim Osborne, Ted Richards, Larry Rippee, Joe Schenkman & Spain.

San Fransisco Comics Vol 1 No.5 - 1979
Joel Beck, John Burnham, Kim Deitch, Bill Griffith, Jay Lynch, Jim Osborne, Trina Robbins, Robin Williams, Gary Arlington and William Murphy

San Fransisco Comics Vol 1 - No. 6 - 1981
